" This is a modified form of a snippet found here:
"
" http://stackoverflow.com/questions/235439/vim-80-column-layout-concerns
"
" I like to keep my lines to 78 columns or less.  This highlights any
" portion of a line that exceeds that length in red.
highlight OverLength ctermbg=red ctermfg=white
match OverLength /\%79v.\+/
